round.unlock_tips2: Finish the last round of quest first!
round.unlock: The last round of quest is not completed and is currently locked
round.lock_desc: Each completed round of quests will move on to the next round.
round.help1:
1. During the event period, you can receive the corresponding rewards by performing a specified number of Advanced Summons in the Hall of Heroes.

2. There will be multiple rounds of quests during the event period, complete the previous round to unlock the next round of quests.

3. The event resets from time to time.
round.help2:
1. During the event period, you can receive the corresponding rewards by performing a specified number of summons in the Oracle Temple.

2. There will be multiple rounds of quests during the event period, complete the previous round to unlock the next round of quests.

3. The event resets from time to time.
round.help3:

2. There will be multiple rounds of quests during the event period, complete the previous round to unlock the next round of quests.

3. The event resets from time to time.

round.help5:
